Step into the world of interstellar  travel,  where
Space Pirates lurk at every corner. Kaptain  Brawe,
a Space Police officer will  embark  on  a  journey
filled with quests, conspiracies and general chaos,
as he follows  the  lead  of  two  kidnapped  alien
scientists.  Set  in  a   beautiful,   hand   drawn
alternative 19th  century  world,  Kaptain  Brawe's
cartoon appearance will suit younger,  as  well  as
mature  players,  who  enjoy  games   filled   with
humorous storyline and challenging puzzles.
